    "thesis": {
        "statement": "IoT Paper 1 formalised forward intent governance (specify, select, monitor), but the operational lifecycle is incomplete. Intent capture is treated as prompt engineering rather than architectural governance input, and reasoning failure diagnosis lacks intent-awareness. We present the IoT Lifecycle: a closed-loop system from capture through retrospective judgement, with governance-proportional correction."
    },
